# Version DOI (v1.6.1, EMSE Option B): 10.5281/zenodo.20645248
cff-version: 1.2.0
type: software
title: "Visual Oracle Bench (Phase 1): A Two-Judge Synthetic-HTML Pilot for LLM-as-Judge Visual Regression Detection with Specificity Reporting"
abstract: >-
  Companion software, datasets, and analysis pipeline for the Empirical
  Software Engineering submission "Visual Oracle Bench (Phase 1): A
  Two-Judge Synthetic-HTML Pilot for LLM-as-Judge Visual Regression
  Detection with Specificity Reporting." Includes the 600-pair Phase 1
  corpus (400 defect pairs + 200 identical-image controls, manifest v2),
  the 6-primitive defect-injection library, capture orchestrator, pixel
  SSIM and perceptual-hash oracles, LLM-as-judge wrappers with both
  API-key and OAuth/subscription access paths, the silent-fabrication
  detection filter, and the paired-test analysis scripts. Judgment
  parquets are released including the contaminated pre-correction
  originals, retained for audit.
